         C          Bb    F\nWhat made you want to live this kind of life?"\n \n[Chorus]\n G                                 Bb C F\nHe said "There ain't no rest for the wicked,\n G                     Bb C F\nMoney don't grow on trees.\n   G\nI got bills to pay,\n       Bb C F\nI got mouths to feed,\n            G                       Bb C F\nThere ain't nothing in this world for free.\n         G\nI know I can't slow down,\n   Bb C F\nI can't hold back,\n            G                  Bb C F\nThough you know, I wish I could.\n          G                      Bb C F\nNo there ain't no rest for the wicked,\n         G                    Bb C F\nUntil we close our eyes for good".\n \n[Verse 3]\n          G\nNow a couple hours passed\n               Bb\nAnd I was sitting at my house,\n            C          Bb    F\nThe day was winding down and coming to an end.\n          G\nSo I turned on the TV\n               Bb\nAnd flipped it over to the news,\n            C          Bb    F\nAnd what I saw I almost couldn't comprehend.\n          G                                      Bb\nI saw a preacher man in cuffs he'd taken money from the church,\n            C          Bb    F\nHe's got this bank account with righteous dollar bills.\n               G\nBut even still I can't say much\n               Bb\nBecause I know we're all the same,\n            C          Bb    F\nOh yes we all seek out to satisfy those thrills.\n \n[Chorus]\n G                                 Bb C F\n"Oh, there ain't no rest for the wicked,\n G                  Bb C F\nMoney don't grow on trees.\n   G\nI got bills to pay,\n       Bb C F\nI got mouths to feed,\n             G                       Bb C F\nThere ain't nothing in this world for free.\n         G\nOh no we can't slow down,\n   Bb C F\nWe can't hold back,\n            G                  Bb C F\nThough you know, we wish we could.\n          G                      Bb C F\nNo there ain't no rest for the wicked,\n         G                    Bb C F\nUntil we close our eyes for good".	875b22ed-1cab-4c6c-bb75-00ecba69f726	2020-09-07 15:53:14.847825	2020-09-07 15:53:14.847825
