un to turn\n         Am\nAnother lesson that has gone unlearned\n             C                G/B       Am\nBut this is not a cry for pitty or for sympathy\n \nG                       Am\nI guess I take after my mother	c3a6f746-0f46-4860-b6d0-d311fdc8fefa	2020-09-10 18:14:16.043569	2020-09-10 18:14:16.043569
